Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼我忘掉那個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}無意識中把它無視了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我居然會…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.84,0:02:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為了順應結局而扭曲了過程嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我居然會…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}奉太郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}奉太郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 等等啊 奉太郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.06,0:02:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.52,0:02:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 有點事想問一下你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:02:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}摩耶花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:02:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}她說她要去漫畫研究社
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那正好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}千反田也好像回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就是說這話不想被伊原和千反田聽到囉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.58,0:03:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在大家面前總覺得有點那啥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}剛剛的詭計
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你認為是本鄉學姐的本意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還是說這是奉太郎的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}本鄉的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嘛～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}奉太郎 我不認為這個手法是本鄉的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我雖然不知道正解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是能肯定不是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你好像有什麼根據啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有這麼致命的矛盾我卻沒發現嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我覺得現在這樣很好並不是騙你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但這卻不是本鄉學姐的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}知道敘述詭計嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}利用有局限視點的文字來欺騙讀者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:03:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就像那部電影裡攝影師其實是犯人就是敘述詭計
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}的確 是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}奉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}作為一個外行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}本鄉學姐用來學習推理的書是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}福爾摩斯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒錯 本鄉學姐只讀過福爾摩斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}聽好了 奉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}敘述詭計不存在於福爾摩斯的小說中
